Name: Captain Collision
About the game: A hostile fleet pursues you through an asteroid field. Your vessel is slow and unarmed. They don't stand a chance. Click and drag asteroids to defend yourself and demolish your enemies. Outflank point-defense systems, intercept homing missiles, and overpower massive bosses as you fight through 5 sectors and restore peace to the galaxy! FEATURES -25 levels -5 bosses -5 bonus waves -Original soundtrack
